<h2>About the Outspoken Ninja</h2>
<div id="storybook" style="width:auto;">
  <div id="storyblob" style="padding-right: 405px;">
    <div style="float: left; width: auto; position: relative;">
      <h3>Lifestyle Support Technologies</h3>
      <p>The goal of the Outspoken Ninja is simple. Provide useful information about products, to our members.</p>

      <p>Using cutting edge search technologies, ratings aggregation and member feedback, our goal is to bring together the information you need to make important decisions about products and servies *you* are interested in.</p>

    <h3>How we got started.</h3>
    <p>Outspoken Ninja is brain child of Silicon Valley entrepreneurs David DeMartini and Shawn Ooi.</p>
    <p>Shawn and David are avid collectors of automobiles and motorcycles, as are many people around the world.  Finding those interesting and unique vehciles was a hassle.  Either the search engines would bring up old ads, bring up irrelevant items, or just not have the national, or international reach desired to find what they were looking for.</p>
    <p>The Ninja Vision is to build tools to support these <s>habits</s> hobbies.  Soon you will be able to test the very same tools Shawn and David, and a select few family and friends have used to find vehicles faster, across the nation (and soon the world), with the click of a single button.</p>
    <p>This is what being a modern day cyber Ninja is about.  Soon you'll be able to be one too.!</p>
    </div>
